description: The construction of 14, three to six storey blocks, incorporating balconies, on part of Silwood Estate (Phases 4a & 4c), North of Silwood Street SE16, comprising a total of 112 one bedroom and 188 two bedroom self-contained flats, 1 two bedroom, 6, three bedroom and 3, four bedroom houses, associated landscaping, provision of cycle and refuse stores and 203 car parking spaces and the formation of new access roads.
